SmileCX WebRTC for Android

This distribution contains modified versions of WebRTC and related third-party components.

===============================================================================

MODIFICATIONS

This distribution includes WebRTC source code that has been modified by SmileCX.
Modifications include:

1. Native (JNI) symbol prefixing:
   - JNI method names prefixed with package path: Java_cx_smile_org_webrtc_*
   - Native library renamed: libscxjingle_peerconnection_so.so
   - Package prefix added to generated JNI headers

2. Java package relocation:
   - Original packages: org.webrtc.*
   - Relocated packages: cx.smile.org.webrtc.*
   - Applied via Gradle Shadow plugin during distribution build

3. Build system modifications:
   - Modified BUILD.gn files to support custom package prefixes
   - Modified JNI code generation scripts and templates
   - Modified build_aar.py to output custom AAR filename

All modifications are documented in the repository:
- Source patches: patches/jni_prefix_smile.patch
- Build scripts: scripts/
- Distribution build: android-scx/

The modifications are designed to prevent symbol collisions when this WebRTC
library is used alongside other WebRTC implementations in the same application.

